# Ignore runtime state
**/.cache/
**/*.log
**/*.pid
**/.DS_Store

# Ignore model payloads and generated model metadata
**/*.gguf
**/*.safetensors
**/*.safetensors.index.json
**/config.json
**/tokenizer.json
**/tokenizer_config.json
**/generation_config.json
**/chat_template.jinja
**/preprocessor_config.json
**/video_preprocessor_config.json
**/model.safetensors
**/model-*.safetensors
**/merges.txt
**/vocab.json
**/LICENSE
**/README.md
**/.gitattributes
**/.gitignore

# Keep the repo's docs and scripts trackable
!/README.md
!agents.md
!Get Started.md
!**/start.sh
!**/stop.sh
